{"tid":2101863,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【BNO方舟】諗住走嘅香港人，你唔好一走了之！","createTime":"2020-07-10T05:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T09:40:37.000Z","uid":90735,"like":62,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb7048d698b3f503f15dfa6e605c7849eb724fb","tid":2101863,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"當你哋興高采烈討論BNO走人嘅時候，我知道執意留守嘅前線勇武一定覺得心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你叫佢哋一齊走？<br />\n<span class=\"small\">佢哋可能仲未被捕、保釋唔到、或學歷唔高，過唔到美加搵庇護</span><br />\n<br />\n我寫呢篇文，係想安慰心淡嘅人：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">既然走難係大勢所趨，我哋要認真思考：<br />\n走難如何有助本地抗爭？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">1. 完全撤走個人資產</span></strong><br />\n當每個人帶走最低20萬，假設20萬人走，都帶走至少400億<br />\n而連登仔不失高大靚仔有車有樓，分分鐘帶幾球走，對港共嚟講，係黃色經濟層面嘅核彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">2. 去英國，創造職位、貢獻GDP</span></strong><br />\n個個諗住洗大餅、開餐館，咁同中国人鬥起油站故事有乜分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一步：爭取資格互認，令到會計、法律、醫療、教育等等人才嘅資格得到承認<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二步：開設自己嘅會計行、律師行、診所，創造職位，請返香港人做文員<br />\n向當地政府申請教育funding開學校<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲未計好多行業可以創業，大家有乜意見？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">3. 爭取冇BNO嘅黃絲、前線一同享受移民權利</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">5. 保留香港文化</span></strong><br />\n電影、音樂、文學、香港話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">6. 光復後，如何吸引香港人回流建港？</span></strong><br />\n根據香港人嘅惰性，去到外地落地生根唔會再返香港，要諗下政策點樣吸引人回流？<br />\n專才回流稅務優惠？回流人士居屋？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>7. 九月投完票先好走，多你一票好多</strong></span><br />\n除非你係白票黨，隨時走都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係嗰句，中共千方百計想控制議會去推agenda<br />\n你投啱票，踢走港共、踢走廢泛民，兩樣嘢可以同時做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">最後送上：<br />\n沈旭暉教授+嘉賓高廣垣 談海外建港</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbziAhRY4eXE&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=f1f2e95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE</a>"},{"pid":"e18b5871fecdd96a3c224fefc11a1efd6491f054","tid":2101863,"uid":90735,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"唔好就咁就走咗去"},{"pid":"c533c28750787803449fd41ed435e9ee7baca9e0","tid":2101863,"uid":242393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzRPJfW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzRPJfW.jpg&h=c3aff8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0OiBAW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0OiBAW.jpg&h=eb5af54a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58862d1f45f25d669c9dd0b20e9c88413eded32c","tid":2101863,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"幫手推，一齊討論<br />\n<br />\n有多啲討論先上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17186453584a0cbb0b0ba50826529523c4f1f750","tid":2101863,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df7a137cab3bb19b54ec3599f17050d90bd2025","tid":2101863,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face